npm install bcrypt cloudinary cookie-parser cors dotenv express express-fileupload express-rate-limit jsonwebtoken mongoose multer nodemailer

bcrypt → password hashing

cloudinary → image upload / storage

cookie-parser → cookies read करायला

cors → frontend-backend connection allow

dotenv → .env file variables

express → Node.js backend framework

express-fileupload / multer → file upload

express-rate-limit → API rate limit security

jsonwebtoken → JWT authentication

mongoose → MongoDB connection

nodemailer → email sending